abstract: The Revlon model on how she maintains her stunning good looks.
snippet: The Revlon model on how she maintains her stunning good looks.
lead_paragraph: Her full name is Anne Vyalitsyna, but she goes simply by Anne V. Based in Los Angeles, she's the face of Revlon's latest: the Expressionist Collection, which will be in stores Oct. 15. As we got started on a photo shoot with the photographer Cameron Krone at Manhattan's Lambs Club, I managed to pick up some tips on how she maintains her stunning good looks.
